# Asset Register (Flask)
- App code under `asset-register/`; 11 SQLite tables (see `database.py` TABLE_ORDER). Use the word **table** (not workspace) in UI and APIs.
- Production DB: `DATABASE_PATH` / `/opt/asset-register/data/asset_register.sqlite` (Terraform backups).
- API routes under `/api/tables/...`; validate `table_name` against `ALLOWED_TABLES`; use parameterized queries and quoted identifiers where needed.
